* fix: hibernate lazy load in context loader

* fix: restore flush moved for testing

fix: Internal server error in /trackedEntityInstances/query when there are no filterable attributes [ DHIS2-13076 ] [ 2.38 ] (#12242)

* fix: illegal argument when missing filterable attributes, clean code

* fix: e2e not supported
